# 🛡️ My Cybersecurity Notes

Welcome to my digital notebook — where I document my journey through OverTheWire, CTFs, and everything I learn about cybersecurity.

I'm Ihtisham, a 4th-semester cybersecurity student at AWKUM. This site is where I write things down so I don't forget them.

**👉 Live Site:** [ihtishamaliamir.github.io](https://ihtishamaliamir.github.io)

